{"tid":1721243,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"重要更新：以後打怪區唔可以再掛機","createTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:06.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-27T14:13:01.000Z","uid":302,"like":76,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"4fbfe681d7aeead0e410dce39caf5713c6faf03b","tid":1721243,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:06.000Z","msg":"一係你就打怪(啲怪高你幾倍lv 重血)或者做任務 <br />\n就唔好掛機 掛機超過十分鐘被gm 踢ok?<br />\n一係你就返據點幫手 一係就去組隊接任做<br />\n除非你真係好撚高lv 好撚高技既 咁你去搵怪打<br />\n掛機係唔會升到lv架 返黎可能已經死左 等重生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n據點既定義 係啲怪入唔到黎 <br />\n就算入黎都要好撚困難 eg暴力基地<br />\n<br />\n認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唔認同<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a0bd8d912dd5e676df3abc0431cbac5d086afda","tid":1721243,"uid":302,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:13:30.000Z","msg":"最重要係你掛機冇戰略上既意義"},{"pid":"8b325febb37ec4d0c919ef0fa48e1104da70f170","tid":1721243,"uid":302,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:14:30.000Z","msg":"你話有戰略上既意義 好似二橋或者尚德村入口咁<br />\n係守城 完全唔同"},{"pid":"7a9d5be3ae3e53a534ef5419c35640e90d725097","tid":1721243,"uid":302,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:14:57.000Z","msg":"其他街 掛機要諗清楚"},{"pid":"982e7d395c4bc8bb5b4d4a78a0de132b972578c6","tid":1721243,"uid":190793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:01.000Z","msg":"借個位<br />\n［韓國戰線］青瓦台請願聯署 同我簽爆佢 （教學）<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1720736\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1720736</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"ea778fef0f2c58ba0a6b42ee4d233e92e270b7e3","tid":1721243,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-14T15:15:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.